@subsubsection Writing your source file


In this example we will assume your source file is called @code{foo.scm}:

<enscript highlight=scheme> ;;; foo.scm

(define (fac n)

@verbatim
 (if (zero? n)
     1
     (* n (fac (- n 1))) ) )
@end verbatim
(write (fac 10)) (newline) </enscript>

