@end verbatim
Escapes all special characters in @code{STRING} with @code{\}, so that the string can be embedded into a regular expression.

<enscript highlight=scheme> (regexp-escape "^[0-9]+:.*$") =>  "\\^\\[0-9\\]\\+:.\n.\\*\\$" </enscript>

